(:summary    "Major mode providing a spectre mode hook for fontification"
 :created    "2003"
 :updated    "20070103"
 :authors    (("Wouter De Cock" . "wouter.decock@esat.kuleuven.ac.be")
	      ("Geert Van der Plas" . "geert_vanderplas@email.com"))
 :maintainer ("Wouter De Cock" . "wouter.decock@esat.kuleuven.ac.be")
 :provided   (active-file ntlst-aux ntlst-section spectre-mode)
 :required   ((("emacs-core" font-lock)
	       ("speedbar" speedbar)))
 :keywords   (affirma spectre\ files)
 :homepage   "http://spice-mode.4t.com"
 :commentary "\
Most of the code of this mode was shamelessly stolen from eldo-mode
(Manu Rouat & GVdP) and spice-mode (Geert Van der Plas & Manu). Language
syntax was provided by Wouter, code and regexps written by Geert.

